# Build-artifact drop for the enterprise image (EDITION=enterprise).
#
# Place the kyde-enterprise wheel here before building the enterprise image:
#   (in ../gateway-enterprise)  python -m build --wheel
#   cp ../gateway-enterprise/dist/kyde_enterprise-*.whl ./wheels/
#
# The wheel is PROPRIETARY — it is gitignored and must never be committed to
# this (public) repo. This directory stays empty for starter builds.
